text.tspan: Style Choice: Monocle menu items and other text primarily consist of lower case typography. This is a style
choice. Lowercase text is often more "approachable" and gives a brand a whimsical feel. Monocle is meant
to be very accessible and approachable to all, so lower case is the primary font case utilized. Note:
sentence casing is used as needed for documentation or other UIs for clarity.
